Discover premier apartment living at ArtHouse, located just a block up from Seattle's stunning waterfront, where you'll fall in love with floor-to-ceiling windows, landscaped terraces, a pet-friendly patio, vibrant design on every floor and sparkling Puget Sound views around every corner.

Soak in the beauty of your quintessentially PNW outdoor surroundings, where the indoors feel like walking the walls of a giant art gallery. ArtHouse offers bold, beautiful living, inside and out.

description: Embrace the Seattle lifestyle at Angeline Apartments. Experience a world of cultures, traditions, ethnicities, and customs. At Angeline, you're a part of the vibrant, rich community of historic Columbia City. Boasting a walk score of 95, our location around the corner from the neighborhood business district can't be beat. We're a 7-minute walk to the light rail, which zips to Downtown Seattle in just 15 minutes. The beach at Seward Park is a 10-minute drive away.

description:
Ask us about our newly renovated homes! When you live at Belmont Court Apartments, you can come home with confidence. We offer spacious units here in our vibrant and upbeat neighborhood of Capitol Hill. Call today for more information on our apartments that offer views of the Seattle city skyline, the Olympic Mountains or of the Puget Sound. Our units here feature full kitchens which include a full size fridge, 4 burner stove/oven, microwave, dishwasher and washer/dryer in unit.
Belmont Court Apartments offers studio, one bedroom, and two bedroom apartments , ranging from less expensive and affordable to luxury. When it comes to your home, you deserve the best and Belmont Court Apartments is excited to help you find your new home!
